titles.title: To provide for the liquidation or reliquidation of certain entries relating to high-density laminate panels entered from 1997 through 2005.
To provide for the liquidation or reliquidation of certain entries relating to high-density laminate panels entered from 1997 through 2005.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.

bill.summary: Directs the Bureau of Customs and Border Protection to provide for the liquidation or reliquidation of certain entries relating to high-density laminate panels.
